# Cloudflare Pages headers.
#
# Two concerns mixed in this file:
#   1. CACHING — /assets/* are content-hashed and safe to cache for a
#      year. /index.html must always re-validate so members boot the
#      newest bundle after a deploy (otherwise the edge can serve stale
#      HTML pointing at old asset hashes and the app boots blank).
#   2. SECURITY (v0.16.0, audit finding #5) — baseline security
#      headers on every response. Applied with a `/*` matcher so every
#      route inherits them; the more specific blocks below add or
#      override as needed.
#
# CSP notes:
#   - `script-src 'self'` is restrictive — Vite-built bundles are all
#     same-origin under /assets/. If a future feature inlines a script
#     it will break, surfaced by a console error; switch to a nonce
#     pattern at that point rather than relaxing globally.
#   - `style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'` is needed because the codebase
#     uses React inline-style attributes everywhere. Browsers check
#     inline `style="..."` against `style-src`. Removing 'unsafe-inline'
#     would require eliminating every style={...} prop.
#   - `connect-src` whitelists the Supabase project + any
#     *.supabase.co for storage/realtime. The wildcard is project-ref-
#     anchored, not blanket *.
#   - `img-src` allows data: (used for inline-encoded SVGs in some
#     icons) and https: (member profile photos via Supabase Storage
#     signed URLs and the occasional external image in club branding).
#   - `frame-ancestors 'self'` is the clickjacking guard. Stricter than
#     X-Frame-Options because it lets the same-origin admin embed work
#     while blocking everyone else.
#
# HSTS:
#   - 1-year max-age. NOT including `preload` yet — that requires a
#     formal submission to the HSTS preload list and is hard to undo.
#     If we want preload later, add it and submit at
#     https://hstspreload.org.

/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=(self), interest-cohort=()
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data: https:; font-src 'self' data:; connect-src 'self' https://exddcpqfdkyxommkslag.supabase.co wss://exddcpqfdkyxommkslag.supabase.co https://*.supabase.co; frame-ancestors 'self'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'

/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/index.html
  Cache-Control: no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate
